Log of the principal changes to the DSAS

Version 3.0.6 (14 Jun 2024)
- Increase memory for php to allow larger log files
- Document that the user should use 'su tc && sudo sh' ti become root 

Version 3.0.5 (31 May 2024)
- Add "-D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release" to ClamAV build, save 60MBytes !
- Minor radius domain fix for Microsoft AD

Version 3.0.4 (24 May 2024)
- Update Linux-PAM (1.5.3 -> 1.6.1)
- Update ClamAV (1.3.0 -> 1.3.1)
- Update curl (8.5.0 -> 8.7.1)
- Update GnuPG (2.4.4 -> 2.4.5)
- Update libgpg-error (1.48 -> 1.49)
- Update libassuan (2.5.6 -> 2.5.7) 
- Update Npth (1.6 -> 1.7)
- Update libtalloc (2.4.1 -> 2.4.2)
- Update OpenSSH (9.6p1 -> 9.7p1)
- Update Zchuck (1.3.1 -> 1.4.0)
- Add pam-modules to allow use of pam_regex.so
- Correct treatment of debian architectures
- Add possibility to add domain name to radius authentification requests 
- Test certificates need to be anti-dated with openssl 3.x

Version 3.0.3 (23 Apr 2024)
- Bump version
- Use 'mktemp -u' in checkfiles to avoid early creation of files

Version 3.0.2 (23 Apr 2024)
- Update osslsigncode (2.7 -> 2.8)
- Add -ignore-crl flag to osslsigncode
- Audit permission of dsas_type on startup

Version 3.0.1 (04 Mar 2024)
- Timeout looking for upper machine correctly

Version 3.0.0 (01 Mar 2024)
- Bump version to 3.0.0
- Update Tinycore 14.0 -> 15.0
- Add package icu74 needed for node build
- Update libtalloc build to use python3.9

Version 2.1.1 (29 Feb 2024)
- Bump version number
- Add ability to quit endless loop on install if upper machine is missing.
- Update openssh (9.5p1 -> 9.6p1)
- Update libgpg-error (1.47 -> 1.48)
- Update libskba (1.6.5 -> 1.6.6)
- Update Gnupg (2.4.3 -> 2.4.4)
- Update ClamAv (1.2.0 -> 1.3.0)
- Update OpenSSL (3.2.0 -> 3.2.1)

