- Update py3.9cairo (1.24.0 -> 1.25.1)
- Update rust (1.72 -> 1.74.1)
- Update node (18.17.1 -> 20.10.0)
- Update PHP (8.0 -> 8.2)

Version 2.0.1 (10 Nov 2023)
- Update osslsigncode (2.6.0 -> 2.7.0)

Version 2.0.0 (15 Sep 2023)
